reviewText: Do not order this if you live in the United States!!! We received the DVDS and my son was so excited. We went to put it in the DVD player, only for it to display a message about a regional code.
Doesn't even play in this region.. WTF lol
Super fast shipment. Love the DVD.
this is a awesome Scooby-Doo movie it is fun and enjoyable to watch. if you have not seen this movie then i recommend you do
